item.title: CVE-2022-4058|2024-08-03T01:27:54.541Z -- unknown -- photo%20gallery%20by%2010web
item.description: The Photo Gallery by 10Web WordPress plugin before 1.8.3 does not validate and escape some parameters before outputting them back in in JS code later on in another page, which could lead to Stored XSS issue when an attacker makes a logged in admin open a malicious URL or page under their control.
